\det\exp=\exp\mathrm{tr}
\det\exp
   \det(I-tA) = \det \exp\log(I-tA) = \exp\mathrm{tr}\log(I-tA) 
   \log(I-tA) = -\sum_{k\ge1} \frac1k t^k A^k, 
   \exp\mathrm{tr}\log(I-tA)    = \exp\left( -\sum_{k\ge1} \frac1k t^k \mathrm{tr}(A^k)\right) 
